{"ID":"20260305082130-bx1sgbd","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-bx1sgbd","tags":"课程/CPP程序设计","title":"运算符重载","type":"doc","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082201-3m4rjar","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","Properties":{"id":"20260305082201-3m4rjar"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"eWFtbA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"---\ntags:\n  - 课程/CPP程序设计\ntitle: 运算符重载\ndate created: 星期日, 十月 19日 2025, 12:47:03 凌晨\ndate modified: 星期二, 十月 21日 2025, 1:22:28 下午\n---"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-3q498qk","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-3q498qk","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1 运算符概述"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-3ld8ezq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-3ld8ezq","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"设有 A 类的对象 a、b、c，要完成赋值操作 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"a.assign(b);"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"assign"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 的定义形式应该是 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"A \u0026amp; assign(const A \u0026amp;t);"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。这样支持临时对象赋值与连续赋值。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-x44kc7p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-x44kc7p","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"类似的，可以使用赋值运算符函数 "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"A \u0026amp; operator=(const A \u0026amp;t);"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-ryrgyfy","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"CodeBlockFenceChar":96,"CodeBlockFenceLen":3,"CodeBlockOpenFence":